          "@@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is the infinite canvas (Penney mode)?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@@type": "Answer",
            "text": "The infinite canvas (Penney mode) provides unlimited canvas space with pan and zoom capabilities. It's perfect for large-scale projects, extensive brainstorming sessions, and creative work that requires unlimited space. All drawing tools are available in infinite mode with collaborative editing support."
