          "@@type": "Question",
          "name": "Can I use CFD Penney offline?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Yes, you can use the whiteboard and drawing features locally without an internet connection. However, collaboration features (real-time sync, video calls, chat) require an internet connection for server-based communication."
