          "@@type": "Question",
          "name": "How do I join a collaboration session?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@@type": "Answer",
            "text": "To join a session, you need the 5-character session code from the host. Enter the code in the join field on the homepage or in the collaboration modal. You'll connect instantly via SignalR."
